comments: Pelle (PHI) makes contact to Hernandez's (TOR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hernandez (TOR) maintains legal guarding position on Pelle (PHI) on the perimeter.
Neto (PHI) makes contact to Thomas's (TOR) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Johnson (TOR) briefly places his hand to Korkmaz's (PHI) front at the start of his drive but contact is marginal.
Korkmaz (PHI) loses control of the ball while he is in the frontcourt and regains possession in the backcourt.
Korkmaz (PHI) makes marginal contact with Watson's (TOR) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Pelle (PHI) delivers contact with his leg to Miller (TOR) during the pick and does not give him room to avoid contact.
Miller (TOR) makes contact to Neto (PHI) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) legally contests Johnson's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Hernandez (TOR) moves alongside of Neto (PHI) and makes marginal contact that does not affect his SQBR.
Watson (TOR) is already in Thybulle's (PHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Thybulle (PHI) makes marginal contact to Johnson's (TOR) side as he begins his drive to the basket.
Pelle (PHI) cleanly blocks Hernandez's (TOR) shot attempt.
Pelle (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position and does not deliver contact to Johnson (TOR).
Pelle (PHI) commits a take foul on Watson (TOR).
